XXX: this service needs some updated documentation.  
XXX: Here's roughly how to get it building today

1. git clone git://github.com/browserplus/bp-fileaccess
2. cd bp-fileaccess
3. git submodule init && git submodule update
4. mkdir src/build
5. cd src/build
6. cmake ..  (cmake -G "Visual Studio 9 2008" .. on Windows)
7. make  (devenv FileAccessService.sln on Windows)
